SimAgent
public class Dealer extends Citizen
This implementation of the Citizen superclass represents an agent tasked with selling the product to RegularCitizen or TownVisitor. He stocks up on drugs at the MobHeadquarters and sells them at the Street.

  • Method Details

    • action

      public void action​(Map map)
      The behavior of this agent goes as follows:
      • If the time is right Dealer goes out selling drugs.
      • If the Dealer has no drugs in his inventory, he goes to MobHeadquarters
        • If there is enough drugs in the MobHeadquarters he stocks up on them and goes selling.
        • If there is not enough drugs, Dealer waits until there is, and resumes his actions
